Prime Minister Zaev believes that NATO membership will bring many necessary investments to Macedonia, where the unemployment rate is more than 20%.
“I believe that the overwhelming majority will vote for it, because more than 80% of our citizens are in favor of the EU and NATO,” Zaev said after the vote.
